    "title": "Ashok Leyland Asia Pacific Associates is Hiring: Warehouse Manager (Senior)",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Ashok Leyland Asia Pacific Associates. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Warehouse Manager to strengthen our Meerut-based team.\n\nAbout Ashok Leyland Asia Pacific Associates:\nAshok Leyland Asia Pacific Associates is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n• Ensure compliance with transportation regulations and safety standards\n• Optimize delivery routes to reduce cost and improve efficiency\n• Implement cost-saving initiatives in transportation and warehousing\n• Coordinate with warehousing teams for inbound and outbound operations\n• Prepare MIS reports on delivery performance and SLA adherence\n• Coordinate with customer service teams to resolve delivery issues\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in Customs Clearance\n• Proficiency in INCOTERMS\n• Proficiency in Inventory Management\n• Proficiency in Last Mile Delivery\n• Proficiency in Fleet Management\n• Proficiency in Route Optimization\n• Proficiency in SAP SCM\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Flexible working hours\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Learning & development budget\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Meerut, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Ashok Leyland Asia Pacific Associates!",
